latestIgtvVideos.title: 5 EASY TIPS TO BOOST YOUR IMMUNITY DURING LOCKDOWN 💪🏼
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.
Tip #1: Vitamins & Minerals💊
-Vitamin A preserves the integrity of the skin and mucous membranes and forma a protective barrier against disease causing germs 🦠 Natural sources: Spinach🥬,Carrot 🥕, Green Leafy Vegetables.
-Vitamin D is the only Vitamin we can manufacture ourselves. It helps to break the lipid layer of germs and viruses. Natural Sources: Sunlight🌞, Salmon 🐟, Organ Meats.
-Vitamin C is available in citrus fruits such as lemon 🍋,limes, and oranges 🍊.
-Zinc is available in Nuts, Seeds, and Dairy 🥛 🥜 .

Some of the brands I use are Nature’s Way, Pure Nutrition, and Now . You can use whichever you deem suitable.

Tip #2 : Diet 🥗
-Ginger is anti-inflammatory and can reduce symptoms of breathlessness, asthama, colds.
-Garlic is anti microbial and excellent for immunity.
You can also have these immunity juices:
-Amla Juice
-Haldi Juice ( Check out my video for the same)
-Tulsi Juice

Tip# 3: Increase Protein Intake
Chicken 🍗 , fish 🐟 , eggs 🥚 , sprouts 🥗, paneer, tofu

Tip #4: Avoid  Wheat and Gluten 🥖🍞🥐
These are inflammatory foods that can impair immunity. Go in for Jowar/ Bajra instead

Tip #5: Exercise🏋🏻‍♂️
Improved blood circulation means improved immunity. 
Try simple exercises like Yoga 🧘🏻‍♀️, Pranayam and At- Home Workouts.
